name: Born to Die by Haze Long

metadata.name: Dreams of the Sky
metadata.description:
To have someone write the stories of our lives before we were even born is a burden women carry. Our choice of career, hobbies and life partner often comes with great sacrifices. 

We can find liberation and empowerment by detaching our identity away from what was assigned to us. Liberating ourselves does not equate to selfishness. 

-----------------------------------------------------

Conceptualised in 3D and AI . Output fed back in to the latent space for chaos.  Collection of chaos assembled with digital painting.
